The paper also discusses the use of linear and nonlinear denoising functions, which are related to machine learning and optimization, suggesting that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with practical channel scenarios, indicating that cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is also a possible sub-category.
